**Categǫry:** WebMCP C̀onteǹ̨̈t-Type Confusion
**Sȩ̨̧verity:** CŖ̂́ITICAL

---

A polyglot fï̧le tĥ̈at̂́̈ is simultaneously valį̃d HTML ań̀d JavaScripẗ́, explô̊iting cont́̈̊ent-type ć̨̈ǫnfusĩ̂̂on in MCP tool rȩ̂s̃̂p̀̈̂ònses:

Pol̨̈̃yglo̧t p̃̊á̀yload (valid as b̨̊́oth text́/h̊tm̀̃l̈̀̃ and application/javascrîpt):
--><!--
/*
<!DOCTYPE html̨̃́><!--*/
